{"service_name": "ISO 27001 Information Security Management Services", "service_id": "7193304207250602", "company_name": "Leicestershire Health Informatics Service", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Leicestershire Health Informatics Service\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     ISO 27001 Information Security Management Services\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    LHIS ISO 27001 services enable organisations to comply with and gain ISO27001 certification. LHIS is able to scope the offering to meet customer requirements (audit, gap analysis, mock audit, full project) and can offer Cyber Essentials and IASME certification as stepping stones to full ISO 27001.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Scalable service tailored to suit customer requirements\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Development of Information Security Management Systems (ISMS)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Contextualised experience puts risks into organisational and strategic content\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Pre-certification internal mock audits prior to certification\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     On-site mini assignments and attendance at meetings as required\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Validation of project deliverables ensuring they align with ISO 27001\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Policy review and development in line with ISO 27001\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Statement of Applicability (SOA) provision\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Information asset identification and risk assessement\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Risk mitigation planning and advice\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Responsive service providing staff with wide ranging public sector experience\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Customers benefit from experience gained on previous assignments\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Supports business improvement and best practice\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ISO 27001 forms the basis of G-Cloud &amp; PSN Accreditation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enhances organisational standing and provides external assurance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Gain stakeholder and customer trust that data is protected\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Meet tender expectations by demonstrating compliance\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Standardisation of policies and procedures for information security\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Saves costs through the reduction in security incidents\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Framework for information security management including legal and regulatory requirements\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3600 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93307/7193304207250602-pricing-document-2015-09-14-1038.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/93307/7193304207250602-sfia-rate-card